loop quote out - get a quote for the cost of a loop out swap

USAGE:
   loop quote out amt

DESCRIPTION:
   Allows to determine the cost of a swap up front

OPTIONS:
   --conf_target uint  the number of blocks from the swap initiation height that the on-chain HTLC should be swept within in a Loop Out (default: 9)
   --fast              Indicate you want to swap immediately, paying potentially a higher fee. If not set the swap server might choose to wait up to 30 minutes before publishing the swap HTLC on-chain, to save on chain fees. Not setting this flag might result in a lower swap fee. (default: false)
   --verbose, -v       show expanded details (default: false)
   --help, -h          show help
